data.description: What an adorable cottage with a huge yard.  Pretty curb-appeal and very well manicured lawn.  Cute front porch area opens to a large den with tile floors and a woodburning fireplace.  Open concept with large open dining room, ceramic tile flooring throughout, granite countertops, tumbled marble backsplash and upgraded stainless steel appliances.  Beautiful quality cabinets add warmth to this kitchen too.  Large master bedroom with original parquet wood floors, which add a vintage charm to the room.  Large master bedroom closet and tub-shower combo.  Hall bath has original vintage tile and tub which give it added charm.  Step out onto your deck and enjoy the shaded backyard.  This deck is large enough for entertaining too.  Truly a great priced home in a great area of Shreveport!  This is a charmer!
